If you want to use something other than Google Test (e.g. CppUnit or CxxTest) as your testing framework, just change the main() function in the previous section to: intmain(intargc,char**argv){
//ThefollowinglinecausesGoogleMocktothrowanexceptiononfailure,
//whichwillbeinterpretedbyyourtestingframeworkasatestfailure.
::testing::GTEST_FLAG(throw_on_failure)=true;
::testing::InitGoogleMock(&argc,argv);
...whateveryourtestingframeworkrequires...
}
